<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五月，一只漂亮的百灵鸟在绿色的田野上选了一个安全的地点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她建了一个巢，下了蛋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>六月，她的蛋孵化出的小鸟们开始长大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>七月，小鸟们长出了羽毛，但是他们还不能飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，百灵鸟妈妈不得不每天去寻找食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂我，喂我。”小鸟们喳喳地叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从高飞到低，再从低飞到高，直到找到些食物为止。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，当她外出觅食，农夫和他的儿子来到田野散步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们停在百灵鸟鸟巢附近开始交谈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的小麦成熟了。到了收割的时候了。我必须雇些人来收小麦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的儿子看上去很失望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>百灵鸟妈妈看到农夫在自己的鸟巢附近，就尽快赶了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“农夫怎么在这儿？”百灵鸟妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小鸟把农夫的话告诉了妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在要走了吗？我们该去哪儿？”一只小百灵鸟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不用着急。”百灵鸟妈妈回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不用搬走。农夫还没有准备好收获。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>百灵鸟妈妈第二天又出去觅食。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它向左飞，向右飞，再向左，再向右。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她之字形飞过田野时，农夫正在下边和儿子讲话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的小麦成熟了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到了收割的时候了。我要请我的朋友帮我收割小麦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的儿子同意了，但是他看上去还是很失望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>百灵鸟妈妈看到农夫走近自己的巢，便尽快地飞回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“农夫怎么在这儿？”百灵鸟妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小鸟把农夫的话告诉了妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在要搬走了吗？我们要去哪儿？”一只小鸟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不用着急。”百灵鸟妈妈答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不用搬走。农夫还没有准备好收获。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>百灵鸟妈妈每天继续寻找食物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每当低空飞行时，她都近距离观察小麦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她注意到谷粒成熟了，开始从麦秆上往下落了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫也关注着小麦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和他的儿子在田野中散步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫对儿子说：“小麦成熟了。到了收割的时候了。你和我必须收割这些小麦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的儿子看上去不再失望了，他的脸上露出了灿烂的微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“农夫怎么在这儿？”百灵鸟妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小鸟们把农夫的话告诉了妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们现在要搬走了吗？我们要去哪儿？”一只小鸟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，是时候搬走了。”妈妈回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要在远离田野的地方建个新巢。农夫准备好收割了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道？”另一只小百灵鸟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当一个农夫准备亲自收割的时候，就说明他真的做好准备了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>